    "asOf": "2011-09-20",
    "date": "2011-10-07T21:48:30Z",
    "text": "Storm Shelter Tax Relief Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a tax deduction, up to $2,500 in a taxable year, for the cost (including labor)\u00a0of purchasing, constructing, and installing a qualified storm shelter.\u00a0 Terminates such deduction after 2012.\n\nRescinds unobligated funds from the Community Development Fund authorized by the Department of Housing and Urban Development Appropriations Act, 2010 and the Department of Defense and Full-Year Continuing Appropriations Act, 2011."
